Package com.erikartymiuk.badbudgetlogic.predictdataclasses

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PredictDataAccount
    This is the base account "row" in our list of values used in the prediction algorithm After the prediction algorithm is run this row tells us the value of whatever account it is a part of on the date.
    PredictDataBudgetItem
    Predict data for a budget item as used by the prediction algorithm to keep track of when the next loss will take place on any given date along with how much of a loss occurred on that date (if a loss did occur).
    PredictDataLoan  
    PredictDataMoneyGain
    Predict data for the money Gain object as used by the prediction algorithm to keep track of when the next deposit will take place on any given date.
    PredictDataMoneyLoss
    Predict data for the money loss object as used by the prediction algorithm to keep track of when the next loss will take place on any given date.
    PredictDataMoneyOwed
    Predict Data for a moneyOwed object/account.
    PredictDataSavingsAccount
    Predict Data for a savings account.
    TransactionHistoryItem
    Class storing information needed to fully describe a bad budget transaction that occurred.
